<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Life Countdown - Your Remaining Days</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="flex justify-center items-center min-h-screen bg-gray-100">

    <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-6 w-96 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">⏳ Your Remaining Days ⏳</h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-red-600 font-semibold mt-4">
            🚀 You have approximately <span class="font-bold text-black"><%=remaingdays%></span> Days And <span class="font-bold text-black"><%=hour%></span> Hours left!
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 italic">
            "Make every moment count and live life to the fullest!" 🌟
        </p>

        <!-- Action Buttons -->
        <div class="mt-6 space-x-4">
            <a href="/" class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition">
                Try Again 🔄
            </a>
           
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
